item.releaseNotes:
This release contains the following products and updates for CentOS7 and SL6: 
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;dynafed 1.5.0 - improvements and a bug fix http://lcgdm.web.cern.ch/dynafed-150-released-epel&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal 2.16.3 - several bug fixes and improvements https://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/gfal2-2.16.3 &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal-util 1.5.3 - bug fix https://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/gfal2-util-1.5.3&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;davix 0.7.5 -&amp;nbsp; bug fixes and improvements http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/davix-075&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dCache 5.2.5 - new golden release included in UMD https://www.dcache.org/downloads/1.9/release-notes-5.2.shtml &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;APEL 1.8.1 - option to update benchmarks/spec levels using a local configuration option rather than the BDII https://github.com/apel/apel/blob/dev/CHANGELOG &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;XROOTD 4.11.0 - several new features and bug fixes https://github.com/xrootd/xrootd/blob/v4.11.0/docs/ReleaseNotes.txt&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Frontier Squid 4.9.2 - important bug fix http://frontier.cern.ch/dist/rpms/frontier-squidRELEASE_NOTES&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt; 
This release contains also argo-ams-library 0.4.2 for SL6, adding X509  to the AMS client and bringing additional bug fixes https://github.com/ARGOeu/argo-ams-library/releases/tag/v0.4.2

This release includes the following updates:
&lt;h3&gt;SL6&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;StoRM 1.11.14 (SL6 only) - &lt;a href=&quot;http://italiangrid.github.io/storm/2018/07/25/storm-v1.11.14-released.html&quot;&gt;several fixes&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal2 2.16.1 - &lt;a href=&quot;https://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/gfal2-2.16.1&quot;&gt;bug fixes&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal2-python 1.9.5 - &lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/gfal2-python-1.9.5&quot;&gt;bug fixes&lt;/a&gt;, added gfal2-python3&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;davix 0.7.1 - &lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/davix-0.7.1&quot;&gt;bug fixes&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CGSI-gSOAP 1.3.11 - &lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/cgsi-gsoap-1.3.11&quot;&gt;fix on SRM timeout causing&lt;/a&gt; transfer failures on CC7&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;XRootD 4.8.5 - &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/xrootd/xrootd/blob/v4.8.5/docs/ReleaseNotes.txt&quot;&gt;several major and minor fixes&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;yaim-core 5.1.7 - fix for the warning &quot;join&quot; command on CentOS 6/7&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ARC 15.03.19 - &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nordugrid.org/arc/releases/15.03u19/release_notes_15.03u19.html&quot;&gt;bugfix release&lt;/a&gt;, mainly to address how ARC counts HELD jobs in Condor&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;GridSite 2.3.5 - &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/CESNET/gridsite/wiki/Gridsite-release-page#GridSite_235&quot;&gt;bugfix release&lt;/a&gt; addressing formatting and warning fixes. RPM packaging were updated to provide CGI scripts at the same location as native Fedora and EPEL packaging. Project URL has been updated&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;CentOS7&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal2 2.16.1 -&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/gfal2-2.16.1&quot;&gt;bug fixes&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal2-python 1.9.5 -&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/gfal2-python-1.9.5&quot;&gt;bug fixes&lt;/a&gt;, added gfal2-python3&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;davix 0.7.1 -&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/davix-0.7.1&quot;&gt;bug fixes&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CGSI-gSOAP 1.3.11 -&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/cgsi-gsoap-1.3.11&quot;&gt;fix on SRM timeout causing&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;transfer failures on CC7&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;XRootD 4.8.5 -&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/xrootd/xrootd/blob/v4.8.5/docs/ReleaseNotes.txt&quot;&gt;several major and minor fixes&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;yaim-core 5.1.7 - fix for the warning &quot;join&quot; command on CentOS 6/7&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ARC 15.03.19 -&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nordugrid.org/arc/releases/15.03u19/release_notes_15.03u19.html&quot;&gt;bugfix release&lt;/a&gt;, mainly to address how ARC counts HELD jobs in Condor&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;GridSite 2.3.5 -&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/CESNET/gridsite/wiki/Gridsite-release-page#GridSite_235&quot;&gt;bugfix release&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;addressing formatting and warning fixes. RPM packaging were updated to provide CGI scripts at the same location as native Fedora and EPEL packaging. Project URL has been updated&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;

This release contains the following:* SL6&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;APEL 1.5.1 - Add support for Torque 5.1.2 time duration format; change dirq call to use absolute path to support versions of dirq &amp;gt;= 1.7; fix crash when StAR loader encouters a valid XML file with no records in it.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;APEL-SSM 2.1.7 - Added a delay when receiver is reconnecting to improve reliability. Improved the log output for SSM receivers so that there are fewer trivial entries and so it's more useful in tracking messages on the filesystem. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CVMFS 2.3.5 - various bug fixes (see&lt;a href=&quot;http://cvmfs.readthedocs.io/en/2.3/cpt-releasenotes.html&quot;&gt; release notes&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;DynaFed 1.3.1 - various bug fixes and improvements (see &lt;a href=&quot;http://lcgdm.web.cern.ch/dynafed-131-available-epel-testing&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ARC 15.03.14 - bugfix release, previous version 15.03u13 suffering from a memory leak causing crashes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Globus GridFTP 11.8.4 - new build with 2 patches from DPM applied&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dpm-dsi 1.9.13 - bug fix (dpm-gsiftp startup script seen to stop and then report daemon already running); use the new gridftp api to remove hack for gridftp redirection.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Davix 0.6.6 - bug fixes, see &lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/davix-060&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dmlite 0.8.6 - bug fix release bringing &lt;a href=&quot;http://lcgdm.web.cern.ch/dmlite-086-released-epel&quot;&gt;small changes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal2-utils 1.5.0 - &lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/gfal2-util-1.5.0&quot;&gt;bug fixes/improvements&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CERN Frontier squid 3.5.24-3.1 - see &lt;a href=&quot;http://frontier.cern.ch/dist/rpms-debug/frontier-squidRELEASE_NOTES&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ARC nagios-probes 1.9.1 - bug fixes, see &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nordugrid.org/arc/releases/15.03u14/release_notes_15.03u14.html&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;QCG Broker 4.2.0 - added support for Array Jobs; instant information about resources for the new qcg-resources command; bug fixes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal2-python 1.9.2 - see &lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/gfal2-python-1.9.2&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;XROOTD 4.6.1 - &lt;a href=&quot;http://xrootd.org/download/ReleaseNotes.html&quot;&gt;several new features and bug fixes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dCache 3.0.25 - see &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.dcache.org/downloads/1.9/release-notes-3.0.shtml#25&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;FTS 3.6.8 - &lt;a href=&quot;http://fts3-service.web.cern.ch/documentation/releases#qt-release-ui-tabs3&quot;&gt;several new features and bug fixes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;lcgdm 0.18.2 - bug fixes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal2 2.13.4 - Default checksum for local copy was removed&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;* CentOS7&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;APEL 1.5.1 - first release in UMD4/C7. Add support for Torque 5.1.2 time duration format; change dirq call to use absolute path to support versions of dirq &amp;gt;= 1.7; fix crash when StAR loader encouters a valid XML file with no records in it.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;APEL-SSM 2.1.7 - first release in UMD4/C7. Added a delay when receiver is reconnecting to improve reliability. Improved the log output for SSM receivers so that there are fewer trivial entries and so it's more useful in tracking messages on the filesystem. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CVMFS 2.3.5 - first release in UMD4/C7. Various bug fixes (see &lt;a href=&quot;http://cvmfs.readthedocs.io/en/2.3/cpt-releasenotes.html&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;WN 4.0.5 - first release in UMD4/C7&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;DynaFed 1.3.1 - first release in UMD4/C7&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ARC 15.03.14 - bugfix release, previous version 15.03u13 suffering from a memory leak causing crashes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Globus GridFTP 11.8.4 - new build with 2 patches from DPM applied&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dpm-dsi 1.9.13 - bug fix (dpm-gsiftp startup script seen to stop and then report daemon already running); use the new gridftp api to remove hack for gridftp redirection.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Davix 0.6.6 - bug fixes, see &lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/davix-060&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dmlite 0.8.6 - bug fix release bringing &lt;a href=&quot;http://lcgdm.web.cern.ch/dmlite-086-released-epel&quot;&gt;small changes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal2-utils 1.5.0 - &lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/gfal2-util-1.5.0&quot;&gt;bug fixes/improvements&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CERN Frontier squid 3.5.24-3.1 - see &lt;a href=&quot;http://frontier.cern.ch/dist/rpms-debug/frontier-squidRELEASE_NOTES&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ARC nagios-probes 1.9.1 - bug fixes, see &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nordugrid.org/arc/releases/15.03u14/release_notes_15.03u14.html&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;QCG
 Broker 4.2.0 - added support for Array Jobs; instant information about 
resources for the new qcg-resources command; bug fixes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal2-python 1.9.2 - see &lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/gfal2-python-1.9.2&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;XROOTD 4.6.1 - &lt;a href=&quot;http://xrootd.org/download/ReleaseNotes.html&quot;&gt;several new features and bug fixes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dCache 3.0.25 - see &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.dcache.org/downloads/1.9/release-notes-3.0.shtml#25&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ARGUS 1.7.3 - this release introduces support for different X.509 CA Authentication profiles via the new Authentication Profile Policy Information Point (PIP); see &lt;a href=&quot;http://argus-documentation.readthedocs.io/en/stable/release_notes/v_1_7_1.html&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; (NOTICE: 1.7.3 refers to UMD version numbering, so reference to 1.7.1 release notes is correct)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;lcgdm 0.18.2 - bug fixes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal2 2.13.4 - Default checksum for local copy was removed&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;

This release contains the following products: 
&lt;h3&gt;CentOS7&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Davix 0.6.4&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;GFAL 2.12.2&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;GFAL Utils 1.4.0&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CGSI gSOAP 1.3.10&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfalFS 1.5.1&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;srm-ifce 1.24.1&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;yaim core 5.1.4&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;MyProxy 6.1.25&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;globus-default-security 6.4.0&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dCache SRM client 3.0.9&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ARC 15.03.12&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;canL 2.1.8&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;FTS3 3.5.8&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dpm-dsi 1.9.0&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;GridFTP 11.8.1&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;GRAM5 13.16.0&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;SL6&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;GFAL 2.12.2&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;GFAL Utils 1.4.0&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CGSI gSOAP 1.3.10&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfalFS 1.5.1&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;FTS3 3.5.8&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;yaim core 5.1.4&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Davix 0.6.4&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;canL 2.1.8&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dCache SRM client 3.0.9&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;

