&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;CREAM sub-components:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;BLAH 1.16.5: This updates of BLAH fixes a problem with the new BLparser that can happen under high load. It also addresses an issue with the new BLParser with LSF: bhist is not used anymore and therefore the load caused by the bupdater is much lower than before. This new BLAH version also enables the submissions to Torque version 2.5.8&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;

