&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;LCG Utils 1.12.0: Supporting GLUE 2. Return estimatedWaitTime for files in an asyncrhonous SRM request in Python. FTS overwrite changes to improve stat logic before deleting the dest file services.xml usage with is-interface. Other minor bug fixes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;

